title: Zatoichi.Collection.1963-1989.DVDRip.x264-CG
description:
The complete Zatoichi saga between 1963 and 1989. 
All starring the legendary Shintaro Katsu.

These are the best rips I've found so far. Off the superb site Cinemageddon.

DVDRips, x264, japanese audio and English subs.

Recommended player: MPC-HC (just google for "cccp codec") or VLC
